| full name       =Flavius Arcadius Augustus
| title           =[[Eastern Roman Emperor|Emperor]] of the [[Byzantine Empire|Eastern Roman (Byzantine) Empire]]
| image           =[[File:Arcadius Istanbul Museum.PNG|250px|Idealising bust of Arcadius in the Theodosian style combines elements of classicism with the new hieratic style ([[Istanbul Archaeology Museum]])]]
| imgw            =250px
| caption         =Idealising bust of Arcadius in the Theodosian style combines elements of classicism with the new hieratic style ([[Istanbul Archaeology Museum]])
| reign           =January 383 – 395 ([[Augustus (honorific)#In the divided Roman Empire|Augustus]] under [[Theodosius I|his father]]); &lt;br&gt;395 – 1 May 408 (emperor in the [[Eastern Roman Empire|east]], with his brother [[Flavius Augustus Honorius|Honorius]] emperor in the [[Western Roman Empire|west]])
| birth_date   =377/8
| birth_place  =[[Spain]]
| death_date   ={{Death date|408|5|1|df=y}} (aged 30 or 31)
| death_place  =
| place of burial =
| predecessor     =[[Theodosius I]]
| successor       =[[Theodosius II]]
| spouse          =[[Aelia Eudoxia]]
| issue           =[[Theodosius II]] &lt;br /&gt; [[Pulcheria]]
