*[[1947]] &amp;ndash; [[David Leland]], British actor, director and screenwriter
*  1947   &amp;ndash; [[Ken Scott]], English record producer and recording engineer
*  1947   &amp;ndash; [[Björn Skifs]], Swedish singer ([[Blue Swede]])
*  1947   &amp;ndash; [[Andrew Tobias]], American journalist and author
*[[1948]] &amp;ndash; [[Craig Frost]], American musician ([[Grand Funk]] &amp; [[Bob Seger]])
*  1948   &amp;ndash; [[Gregory Itzin]], American actor
*  1948   &amp;ndash; [[Rémy Trudel]], French Canadian politician
*[[1949]] &amp;ndash; [[Veronica Cartwright]], American actress
*  1949   &amp;ndash; [[Toller Cranston]], Canadian figure skater and artist
*  1949   &amp;ndash; [[Massimo D'Alema]], 76th Prime Minister of Italy
*  1949   &amp;ndash; [[Jessica Lange]], American actress
*[[1950]] &amp;ndash; [[Steve Erickson]], American novelist
*  1950   &amp;ndash; [[Alexander Lebed]], Russian general and politician (d. 2002)
*  1950   &amp;ndash; [[Chandra Babu Naidu]], Indian politician
*[[1951]] &amp;ndash; [[Luther Vandross]], American singer (d. 2005)
*[[1952]] &amp;ndash; [[Louka Katseli]], Greek [[Minister for Labour and Social Security (Greece)|Minister for Labour and Social Security]]
*  1952   &amp;ndash; [[Božidar Maljković]], Serbian basketball coach
*[[1953]] &amp;ndash; [[Sebastian Faulks]], British novelist
*[[1954]] &amp;ndash; [[Gilles Lupien]], French-Canadian ice hockey player
*[[1955]] &amp;ndash; [[Don Pettit]], American astronaut and inventor
*[[1956]] &amp;ndash; [[Beatrice Ask]], Swedish politician
*[[1957]] &amp;ndash; [[Geraint Wyn Davies]], Welsh-born Canadian actor
