*[[1959]] &amp;ndash; [[Clint Howard]], American actor
*[[1961]] &amp;ndash; [[Konstantin Lavronenko]], Russian actor
*  1961   &amp;ndash; [[Don Mattingly]], American baseball player
*  1961   &amp;ndash; [[Barry Smolin]], American radio host, writer, and musician
*  1961   &amp;ndash; [[Nicholas Lyndhurst]], British actor
*[[1962]] &amp;ndash; [[Henry Joseph Nasiff Jr.]] (AKA: Hank the Angry Drunken Dwarf), American radio personality (d. 2001)
*[[1963]] &amp;ndash; [[Aubrey de Grey]], British biomedical gerontologist
*  1963   &amp;ndash; [[Maurício Gugelmin]], Brazilian racing driver
*[[1964]] &amp;ndash; [[Crispin Glover]], American actor
*  1964   &amp;ndash; [[Andy Serkis]], English actor
*  1964   &amp;ndash; [[Rosalynn Sumners]], American figure skater
*[[1965]] &amp;ndash; [[Adrian Fernández]], Mexican racing driver
*  1965   &amp;ndash; [[Kostas Hatzidakis]], Greek politician
*  1965   &amp;ndash; [[April March]], American musician
*[[1966]] &amp;ndash; [[David Chalmers]], Australian philosopher
*[[1967]] &amp;ndash; [[Raymond van Barneveld]], Dutch darts player
*  1967   &amp;ndash; [[Lara Jill Miller]], American actress
*  1967   &amp;ndash; [[Mike Portnoy]], American drummer ([[Dream Theater]], [[Avenged Sevenfold]])
*[[1968]] &amp;ndash; [[J. D. Roth]], American game show host and television personality
*  1968   &amp;ndash; [[Yelena Välbe]], Russian cross-country skier
*[[1970]] &amp;ndash; [[Shemar Moore]], American actor
*  1970   &amp;ndash; [[Adriano Moraes]], Brazilian rodeo performer
*  1970   &amp;ndash; [[Sarantuya|Saraa]], Mongolian singer
*[[1971]] &amp;ndash; [[Carla Geurts]], Dutch swimmer
*  1971   &amp;ndash; [[Allan Houston]], American basketball player
*  1971   &amp;ndash; [[Nikos Kyzeridis]], Greek footballer
*[[1972]] &amp;ndash; [[Le Huynh Đuc]], Vietnamese footballer
*  1972   &amp;ndash; [[Carmen Electra]], American actress
*  1972   &amp;ndash; [[Željko Joksimović]], Serbian singer, songwriter and producer
*  1972   &amp;ndash; [[Marko Kon]], Serbian singer, composer, songwriter and producer
*  1972   &amp;ndash; [[Stephen Marley (musician)|Stephen Marley]], Jamaican musician
*[[1973]] &amp;ndash; [[Geoff Lloyd]], British radio presenter
*  1973   &amp;ndash; [[Lamond Murray]], American basketball player
*[[1974]] &amp;ndash; [[Tina Cousins]], English singer
*[[1976]] &amp;ndash; [[Aldo Bobadilla]], Paraguayan football player
*  1976   &amp;ndash; [[Shay Given]], Irish footballer
*  1976   &amp;ndash; [[Joey Lawrence]], American actor
*  1976   &amp;ndash; [[Chris Mason (ice hockey)|Chris Mason]], Canadian ice hockey goaltender
*[[1977]] &amp;ndash; [[John Hugger|Johnny &quot;The Bull&quot; Stamboli]], professional wrestler
*[[1978]] &amp;ndash; [[Mirei Kuroda]], Japanese gravure idol
*[[1979]] &amp;ndash; [[Ludovic Magnin]], Swiss football player
*  1979   &amp;ndash; [[Nathan Marquardt]], American mixed martial artist
*  1979   &amp;ndash; [[Quinn Weng]], Taiwanese singer ([[Seraphim (band)|Seraphim]])
*[[1980]] &amp;ndash; [[Chris Duffy (baseball)|Chris Duffy]], American baseball player
*  1980   &amp;ndash; [[Arin Paul]], Indian Film Director
*  1980   &amp;ndash; [[Jasmin Wagner]], German singer
*[[1982]] &amp;ndash; [[Dario Knežević]], Croatian football player
*[[1983]] &amp;ndash; [[Danny Granger]], American basketball player
*  1983   &amp;ndash; [[Miranda Kerr]], Australian supermodel
*  1983   &amp;ndash; [[Joanne King]], Irish/English actress
*  1983   &amp;ndash; [[Fabio Staibano]], Italian rugby player
*[[1984]] &amp;ndash; [[Tyson Griffin]], American mixed martial artist
*  1984   &amp;ndash; [[Edixon Perea Valencia]], Colombian football player
*[[1985]] &amp;ndash; [[Ehsan Jami]], Dutch-Iranian politician and activist.
*[[1986]] &amp;ndash; [[Cameron Duncan]], New Zealand director (d. 2003)
*[[1987]] &amp;ndash; [[John Patrick Amedori]], American actor
