====East Asia====
*The [[Chinese language]] is written by some [[Hui people|Hui]] in the Arabic-derived [[Xiao'erjing]] alphabet.
*The Turkic [[Salar language]] is written by some [[Salar people|Salar]] in the Arabic alphabet
* [[Sini (script)]]
* [[Xiao'erjing]]

====South Asia====
&lt;gallery&gt;
