* [[Diyarbakır]], [[Lice]], [[Hazro]], [[Kozluk]], [[Hizan|Khizan]], [[Siverek|Sevaverak]], [[Şanlıurfa|Edesia]]
* [[Elazığ|Kharpert]], [[Erzincan|Yerznka]], [[Palu|Balu]], [[Bingöl|Tchapaghjur]], [[Çemişgezek|Chmshkatsag]], [[Akpazar|Peri]], [[Kiğı|Kghi]], [[Tunceli|Dersim]], [[Kemah|Kamakh]]
